item.description:
Join me for an afternoon of papercrafting fun!! Bring your latest project. I have lots and lots of great tools, stamps and inks that you are welcome to use. If you don't have a current project I have lots of cards and scrapbooks available for inspiration! Check out some of my card kits on my blog. www.stampinwtithmarilyn.com.

Have you been to one of our meetups yet? If not we would love to meet you!

Marilyn
item.name: Bring Your Own Project - Papercrafting Day
